{"tid":1604049,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[請廣傳]新五大訴求","createTime":"2019-09-30T00:22:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T15:11:00.000Z","uid":323301,"like":11,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"85813f119434a672f3e7068281b680e79ad131fa","tid":1604049,"uid":323301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T00:22:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1. 林鄭下台<br />\n2. 收回暴動定性<br />\n3. 釋放被補示威者<br />\n4. <span style=\"color: red;\">*重組警隊，成立獨立調查委員會</span><br />\n5. 全港一人一票雙普選</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">*簡述第4點<br />\n目的：<br />\n嚴懲每一個暴警，將每一個暴警都送入監牢<br />\n缺一不可！！<br />\n<br />\n做法：<br />\n先解散現有警隊，可調配廉署作臨時警隊，挽回香港警隊。<br />\n由於沒有警員編號，所以「有殺錯，冇放過」(自己攞黎)<br />\n就算不把全港30000+警察革職，至少要<span style=\"color: red;\">解散防暴隊、速龍小隊、所有便衣警員，和所有指揮官</span><br />\n<br />\n解散只係挽回形像，仲要將佢地<span style=\"color: red;\">逐一</span>嚴懲。所以仍然要成立獨立調查委員會，調查<span style=\"color: red;\">每一個</span>暴警，公平審訊，審訊過程有法律約束力，並記錄在案。<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求，缺一不可！<br />\n清算暴警，缺一不可！</span></span>"},{"pid":"5706adc5402b425e0b5f1da4efb45db9657bccb2","tid":1604049,"uid":177013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T00:24:34.000Z","msg":"Push幫你推！ 重組警隊！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0cbef5ea675350085bd6f69bff600399acd3acd","tid":1604049,"uid":3115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T00:24:47.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"f03184c0c239afc2bbe75a9f5b57a3f934f7a3d3","tid":1604049,"uid":64884,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T00:25:03.000Z","msg":"林鄭唔好下台啦<br />\n佢下台咪等於畀中共派個冇咁強硬嘅補鑊<br />\n而家佢得閒就火上加油咪幾好"},{"pid":"7bd9e5bbe3a797e764cde2a2b64f84da2bdeff27","tid":1604049,"uid":220873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T00:25:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e8bc075e568c22b6137c52283f1826ffe5339a57","tid":1604049,"uid":237133,"like":0,"dis